Package com.atlan.api

The various endpoints of the Atlan API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEndpoint  
    ApiTokensEndpoint
    API endpoints for managing Atlan's API tokens.
    AtlasEndpoint
    Base class for all API endpoints that ultimately access the underlying metastore.
    AuditSearchEndpoint
    API endpoints for searching against Atlan's Elasticsearch index for entity changes (activity log).
    EntityBulkEndpoint
    API endpoints for operating on multiple assets (entities) at the same time (in bulk).
    EntityGuidEndpoint
    API endpoints for operating on a single entity, based on its unique ID (GUID).
    EntityUniqueAttributesEndpoint
    API endpoints for operating on a single asset (entity), based on its unique attributes (primarily qualifiedName).
    EntityUniqueAttributesEndpoint.ClassificationList
    Request class for handling classification additions.
    GroupsEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's groups.
    HeraclesEndpoint
    Base class for all API endpoints that ultimately access Heracles-surfaced services.
    IndexSearchEndpoint
    API endpoints for searching against Atlan's Elasticsearch index for all entities.
    LineageEndpoint
    API endpoints for retrieving lineage from Atlan.
    PersonasEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's personas.
    PurposesEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's purposes.
    RequestsEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's requests.
    RolesEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's roles.
    TypeDefsEndpoint
    API endpoints for operating on Atlan's type definitions (in simple terms the underlying metadata model).
    UsersEndpoint
    API endpoints for interacting with Atlan's users.
    WorkflowsEndpoint
    API endpoints for operating on Atlan's workflows.
